description: Seeks to track the investment return of the Bloomberg U.S. 5–10 Year Government/Credit Float Adjusted Index, a market-weighted bond index that covers investment-grade bonds with a dollar-weighted average maturity of 5 to 10 years. Invests in U.S. government high-quality (investment grade) corporate and investment-grade international dollar-denominated bonds. Passively managed, using index sampling.
name: Vanguard Intermediate-Term Bond ETF
